19.
20.
EXT. SUTTER'S WELL - DAY (FLASHBACK)21 21
CAMERA snakes through tall grass then FINDS Sutter, alive and
well, wearing overalls and a straw hat while he ladles water
into his mouth and over his head. A pair of hound-dogs
lounge nearby.
BOY WILLIE (V.O.)
...and things he got around
there...I’m gonna hide and wait
till I catch him looking down his
well just right...then I’m gonna
run over and push him in. A great
big old three-hundred-and-forty-
pound man.
Sutter bends and looks down his well and we PUSH IN FAST.
OMIT22 22
INT. CHARLES HOUSE/PARLOR - DAY23 23
BERNIECE
Well, what he calling your name
for?
BOY WILLIE
He bending over looking down his
well, woman...how he know who
