anybody. Where was you when Sutter
fell in his well? Where was
Doaker? Me and Lymon was over in
Stoner County. Tell her, Lymon.
The Ghosts of the Yellow Dog got
Sutter. That’s what happened to
him.
BERNIECE
You can talk all that Ghosts of the
Yellow Dog stuff if you want. I
know better.
LYMON
The Ghosts of the Yellow Dog pushed
him. That’s what the people say.
EXT. SUTTER'S HOUSE - DAY (FLASHBACK)24 24
We LOOK UP FROM THE BOTTOM OF THE WELL as a ring of
