EXT. CHARLES HOUSE - DAY28 28
CLOSE ON A GOLD CRUCIFIX, glinting in the sunlight. WIDEN TO
REVEAL AVERY walking to the front door. Black and thirty-
eight years old, Avery is honest and ambitious. He is
dressed in a suit and tie with a gold cross around his neck.
He carries a small Bible.
He KNOCKS. Doaker answers and lets him in.
DOAKER
Hey, Avery, come on in.
