With difficulty Boy Willie and Lymon move the piano a bit.
BOY WILLIE (CONT'D)
What you think?
LYMON
It’s heavy...but you can move it.
Only it ain’t gonna be easy.
BOY WILLIE
It wasn’t that heavy to me. Okay
