though! You get on this end. I’ll
carry three hundred and fifty
pounds of it. All you got to do is
slide your end out. Ready?
They switch sides and try again without success. Doaker
enters from his room.
DOAKER
Boy Willie, what you doing?
LYMON
Hey Doaker...how this piano get in
the house?
BOY WILLIE
I’m carrying this piano out the
