Just go on and leave me alone.
Come on, Lymon. I got this end.
STAY WITH Doaker as he goes into his room, opens a drawer and
pulls out a REVOLVER.
In the Parlor Boy Willie and Lymon prepare to move the piano.
LYMON
How we gonna get it in the truck?
