Well, let her find that out then.
If Avery blessing the house is
gonna make her feel better...what
you got to do with it?
AVERY
Berniece say Maretha seen him too.
I don’t know, but I found a part in
the Bible to bless the house. If
he is here then that ought to make
him go.
BOY WILLIE
You worse than Berniece believing
all that stuff. Talking about...if
he here. Go on up there and find
